be.ac.umons.jsonvalidation.graph

Class NodeInGraph<L>

  • java.lang.Object
    • be.ac.umons.jsonvalidation.graph.NodeInGraph<L>
  • Type Parameters:
    L - Location type

    public class NodeInGraph<L>
extends Object
    A node in a KeyGraph. It is labeled by a triplet from the reachability relation. For each location p in the VPA, it has a boolean indicating whether the target state of the triplet can read a return symbol and pop the stack symbol corresponding to p.
